data.description: Incredible opportunity to live in the highly coveted Cathedral Park Neighborhood of St Johns. The midcentury modern residence sits on a massive 12,500 soft corner lot and features a spacious open floor plan, hot tub room, an expansive two car garage, and a porch overlooking the substantial backyard, and RV parking. This North Portland Classic is waiting for your final touches. Enjoy breathtaking views of the iconic St. Johns Bridge, the picturesque West Hills, and seasonal glimpses of the Willamette River all from the comfort of your home. Buyer to verify and conduct all due diligence.
